Disclaimer:
Every user with access to the RAIS data may access this file. This file may NOT leave the server. This file loops around selected years in order to build a yearly municipality panel. Some filters and variables are made available. If you have suggestions on how to improve this code, please contact the current RA. Comments are always welcome!
- Current RA: Bernardo Dias de Aquino Nascimento (bernardo.nascimento@aluno.puc-rio.br)

Instructions:
1) Do NOT edit this file. Copy and paste this code in your personal folder inside the server. You may edit the code inside your folder as needed. For instance, if you wish to build a monthly panel instead of yearly, the code may easily be adapted to that
2) Change the global variables FIRST_YEAR and LAST_YEAR to the years you want to build the panel
3) Change the global variable REGIONS for the regions you want to build the panel
4) Check for variables of interest
5) Run the code
*/
